{"tid":406662,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"酒店主廚教清洗鮑魚　牙刷擦生鮑魚令肉質變韌","createTime":"2017-09-19T23:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T23:50:05.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"29e5eeb5b05fa88a963ba2e009dc204485e05a00","tid":406662,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T23:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1900000/1902088/abalone20170912_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1900000%2F1902088%2Fabalone20170912_1024.jpg&h=b307ba7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n許多新手主婦表示，鮑魚好難洗，就算見街市的鮑魚新鮮都不會買。香港沙田凱悅酒店中菜廳沙田18主廚何振雄師傅，則說一點難度都沒有。他說鮑魚肉和邊位難免會帶點黑色的污穢，當然需要清洗一下。<br />\n<br />\n至於如何清洗？許多人最真接會用牙刷生擦鮑魚，但原來這樣做會令鮑魚收縮，肉質會變韌不好吃。所以依照以下何師傅教大家的洗鮑魚方法，容易又簡單。去片看看：<br />\n<br />\n1.\t煲滾一鍋熱水，然後倒入鮑魚攪拌，約10秒鐘後，就可以撈上來；或者乾脆熄火浸一浸後再撈上來，<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1900000/1902088/20170904_151247_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1900000%2F1902088%2F20170904_151247_1024.jpg&h=60fa6cb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n把鮑魚放入滾水中灼10秒左右。(郭秀芳攝)<br />\n<br />\n2.\t立刻放入凍水中過冷河，<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1900000/1902088/20170904_151317_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1900000%2F1902088%2F20170904_151317_1024.jpg&h=5da2d93d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n滾水灼10秒左右，立刻放入冰水中。(郭秀芳攝)<br />\n<br />\n3.\t用刀仔鎅出鮑魚肉，記得隨手去掉鮑魚的腸臟；<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1900000/1902088/20170904_151503_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1900000%2F1902088%2F20170904_151503_1024.jpg&h=22ee862f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過完冷河，用刀仔鎅甩鮑魚肉。(郭秀芳攝)<br />\n<br />\n4.\t然後用牙刷在水喉下刷鮑魚，慢慢地刷洗，便可擦走那些黑色的污穢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1902088/%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E4%B8%BB%E5%BB%9A%E6%95%99%E6%B8%85%E6%B4%97%E9%AE%91%E9%AD%9A%20%20%20%20%E7%89%99%E5%88%B7%E6%93%A6%E7%94%9F%E9%AE%91%E9%AD%9A%E4%BB%A4%E8%82%89%E8%B3%AA%E8%AE%8A%E9%9F%8C%E3%80%90%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87%E3%80%91?mtc=10019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1902088%2F%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25BA%2597%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25BB%259A%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%25B4%2597%25E9%25AE%2591%25E9%25AD%259A%2520%2520%2520%2520%25E7%2589%2599%25E5%2588%25B7%25E6%2593%25A6%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%25AE%2591%25E9%25AD%259A%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E8%2582%2589%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E8%25AE%258A%25E9%259F%258C%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2589%2587%25E3%2580%2591%3Fmtc%3D10019&d=AOcXI6WYhJzavXyt1VaMMzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=fb9385f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1902088/%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E4%B8%BB%E5%BB%9A%E6%95%99%E6%B8%85%E6%B4%97%E9%AE%91%E9%AD%9A%20%20%20%20%E7%89%99%E5%88%B7%E6%93%A6%E7%94%9F%E9%AE%91%E9%AD%9A%E4%BB%A4%E8%82%89%E8%B3%AA%E8%AE%8A%E9%9F%8C%E3%80%90%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87%E3%80%91?mtc=10019</a>"}]}